Source: mvirt
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Malte <malte@localhost>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), curl
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: mvirt
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: CLI/TUI for mvirt VM management
 Command-line interface and terminal UI for managing virtual machines
 via the mvirt daemon.

Package: mvirt-vmm
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: mvirt VM Manager daemon
 Virtual machine manager daemon that uses cloud-hypervisor to run VMs.
 Includes cloud-hypervisor binary and CLOUDHV.fd UEFI firmware.

Package: mvirt-log
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: mvirt centralized logging service
 Centralized audit logging service for all mvirt components.
 Stores logs in SQLite with many-to-many object relations.

Package: mvirt-zfs
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, zfsutils-linux
Description: mvirt ZFS storage management daemon
 ZFS storage management daemon for mvirt.
 Manages ZFS volumes, snapshots, and templates.

Package: mvirt-net
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: mvirt network management daemon
 Network management daemon for mvirt.
 Manages virtual networks and NICs.
